    {
      "id": "PopularPost33772",
      "post_content": "Kitsune I will take that trade any day of the week.  \n2 life for a point removal spell AND card advantage? How many Lightning Bolts do they have?  \nTo add to the glory, red doesn't have enchantment removal  \nThis card ruins Mono Red Aggro/Burn assuming you have a good late game. This card buys time to get Wrath mana. It effectively makes [hellspark elemental](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=hellspark elemental) a [Flame jab](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flame jab), [Ball Lightning](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ball Lightning) a [Lightning Bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt)  \nThat being said it's a sideboard card at best.",
      "posted_by": "nukeme11",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost33772\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">Kitsune I will take that trade any day of the week.<br/>2 life for a point removal spell AND card advantage? How many Lightning Bolts do they have?<br/>To add to the glory, red doesn't have enchantment removal<br/>This card ruins Mono Red Aggro/Burn assuming you have a good late game.  This card buys time to get Wrath mana. It effectively makes <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"hellspark elemental\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=hellspark elemental\">hellspark elemental</a> a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Flame jab\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flame jab\">Flame jab</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ball Lightning\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ball Lightning\">Ball Lightning</a> a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lightning Bolt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt\">Lightning Bolt</a><br/>That being said it's a sideboard card at best.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '33772'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy7148\">nukeme11</span>\r\n                                (11/5/2009 9:44:46 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\